      <p>I'm Todd. I am an Accessibility Engineer for <a href="https://webstaurantstore.com">WebstaurantStore</a>, I am also a member of the <a href="https://w3.org">W3C</a>. This is my personal site where I write and document what I am doing, where I am speaking, or what conferences I'll be attending. Tech has been a huge part of my life for over forty years from when I started with BASIC and Scheme, and now with React, JavaScript, and Accessibility.</p>
