      <p>I host a podcast, the <a href="https://youtube.com/FrontEndNerdery">Front End Nerdery Podcast</a>. I write articles for publication and I have written articles for Smashing Magazine and CSS-Tricks, and I love food and cooking. Especially lobster and lobster rolls.</p>
